question: Display jazz musicians and rock guitarists who have been in the industry for 10 years.
sql_query1:
SELECT MusicPerformer.Name 
FROM MusicPerformer
WHERE (MusicPerformer.MusicPerformerType = "Jazz Musician" OR MusicPerformer.MusicPerformerType = "Rock Guitarist") AND MusicPerformer.YearsInIndustry = 10
sql_query2:
SELECT MusicPerformer.Name

WHERE MusicPerformer.MusicPerformerType = "Jazz Musician" OR MusicPerformer.MusicPerformerType = "Rock Guitarist" AND MusicPerformer.YearsInIndustry = 10
interpretation1: Which jazz musicians have been in the industry for 10 years and which rock guitarists have been in the industry for the same duration?
interpretation2: Provide a list of all jazz musicians and also provide a list of rock guitarists who have been in the industry for 10 years.
